headline.print_headline: Bahraini Teenager Dies After Clashes With Police: Activists
headline.main: Bahraini Teenager Dies After Clashes With Police: Activists

lead_paragraph: A Bahraini teenager died on Wednesday after clashes between security forces and demonstrators marking the third day of mourning for a young man killed by a bomb blast last week, witnesses and activists said.
